{"tid":1620360,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"驚你未自己戴返個口罩囉","createTime":"2019-10-04T10:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T10:16:01.000Z","uid":273730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8fd368532b5f5716a96a4fc24084ebb1c4d1ecef","tid":1620360,"uid":273730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:09:47.000Z","msg":"最近小弟感冒病左，病左成個禮拜<br />\n咳出來d痰係綠色ge<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我真係好驚戴口罩會比POPO老屈，坐足成年監，所以我聽日會唔戴口罩ga。<br />\n係人多擠逼ge地方又好難忍住唔咳喎。<br />\n如果有廢老叫我戴口罩，咁未同佢講「咁監你係咪代我坐丫？」總之我會喪咳，咳到死都唔會戴返口罩ga。驚你未自己戴返個口罩囉。<br />\n<br />\n病左ge朋友如果驚比人拉，歡迎同我一樣出街唔戴口罩。到時d病毒洗多幾次牌，我相信好快就會出現第二次沙士ga啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b5ebc86762f1cbd582fafa36db8c98c875c707","tid":1620360,"uid":245670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:11:36.000Z","msg":"專去啲多廢老嘅區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b1ab350842cfee1b0531eed776e19d1ecccb2b","tid":1620360,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:16:01.000Z","msg":"我都病鳩左，係咁打乞痴散播細菌，大家記得戴返口罩唔好比我傳染呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}